In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir in vanilla. Stir in KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. Using lightly buttered spatula, press into buttered 3.5 L (13 x 9-inch) pan. To make 18 cm high bunny, shape 3 1/2 cups of mixture for body and 2 cups of mixture for the head. Join head and body with toothpicks to create a bunny. Shape remaining mixture into a ball for the cottontail, roll in coconut and attach to body with a toothpick. Make ears with coloured paper. Cut two slits in the head to attach ears. Create eyes, nose and buttons with miniature marshmallows and gumdrop halves. Use paper for whiskers.